---
By: Dinah M. Craik
Locus:
  Page: 14
  Verse: 3
Tags:
  - Advice
---
The only way to meet affliction is to pass through it solemnly, slowly,
with humility and faith. ...Then its very ways of misery will divide and
become to us a wall, on the right side and the left, until the gulf narrows
before our eyes, and we land on the opposite shore.
